{"tid":6512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"坐肥婆對面食飯好難頂","createTime":"2016-11-27T11:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T14:42:04.000Z","uid":17306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"767ad3d099cb97c6cd224eaa6c6049a72c359faa","tid":6512,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"喺大家樂同條女打邊爐，突然有個龐然巨物走過黎搭檯，原來係一個肥婆同一個普通港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個死肥婆自己唔嗌打邊爐但係又成撚日望住我同條女啲嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個朋友都係打邊爐然後就不斷夾佢朋友啲野黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲同佢個朋友講話：啲肉我幫你清曬佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個fd呆撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似最後只係食得幾條菜同個烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他乜柒都比肥胖搶曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外個肥婆自己嗌左個牛腩飯 佢朋友叫佢比一件黎食都唔撚比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐肥婆對面真係乜柒胃口都冇撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇食曬啲嘢就走左 唔知走左之後個肥婆會唔會食撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9286ddd5bc42798a097e68352075cf77121accf0","tid":6512,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fa0b3451dea5f32120e262eb2ef0272d07403a","tid":6512,"uid":13290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"好撚乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7598f1314ccf8f0e48b8271132d2ae4527507433","tid":6512,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"<b